data.name: label6.Text
data.value:
Images can be added to your document by choosing &Insert -> Image. The image will be inserted at the caret position.
**Note that images are only avaliable when using Rich Text Format (*.rtf) to save**

data.name: label3.Text
data.value:
To choose a font, use the drop-down menus in the Toolbar. This applies for choosing a font size, also.
Alternatively to choose a size, you may choose to use the 'A+' and 'A-' buttons in the Toolbar.
